divs: sighting detailsmy wife and i were looking for shooting stars lying on our backs on the tramp in the back. it was after 1:00am. yes we were sober =) and out of no where a ufo flew over these apartments directly behind our house going exstremly fast....if i had to guess over 100 miles per hour traveling south. this ufo was huge and had no lights on. it appeared to be long almost like a huge battle ship in the sky. it made no engine sound it just made "moving through the air sound". almost like it was solar powered. my wife and i froze in shock of what we had seen. we both saw it and were just amazed and freaked out by it. it was flying in a straight path and in low air space...illegal flying "way to low" but super fast. no lights? never seen anything like it...? fyi: this area has had ufo sightings in past some documented,etc. note: my wife and i know what we saw. it was real! we share it with friends and they think we are crazy ha ha just kidding... well i am sure some do but they haven't came forward... lol sicerely- (name removed to fi field) cms 09\09\11 22:52 cst flg
